<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="that-adv">that <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ðæt/    美 /ðæt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>那么；那样：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’m sorry. I hadn’t realized the situation was that bad.
很抱歉，我没有意识到情况会那么糟糕。</p></div></div>